{"tid":1636443,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[心理戰] 警察犯眾憎 老婆嗌離婚！老豆做走狗 仔女冇朋友！","createTime":"2019-10-07T17:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T02:20:06.000Z","uid":91967,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5628619633720cde17dee8975ce0bc2dc03f07","tid":1636443,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:54:36.000Z","msg":"正所謂，禍必及妻兒。<br />\n<br />\n而加再叫班狗做「黑社會」同「黑警」已經冇用，佢地已經接受咗呢個事實。<br />\n<br />\n但除低制服，佢地都係一班有老婆仔女既狗。要攻擊班賤種，就要攻擊佢地內心最軟嗰Part！<br />\n<br />\n正如「警察OT，老婆3P」係最激到班狗。<br />\n<br />\n所以，以後見到班狗要嗌：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n警察犯眾憎，老婆嗌離婚！<br />\n<br />\n老豆做走狗，仔女冇朋友！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />軟硬兼施，警隊收皮指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfec479a1a9653e3267943557a6c48558b69f4d7","tid":1636443,"uid":91967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:55:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n警察犯眾憎，老婆嗌離婚！<br />\n<br />\n老豆做走狗，仔女冇朋友！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a459ce97c872f042570965ccd4194bae04b23878","tid":1636443,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:55:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n警察犯眾憎，老婆嗌離婚！<br />\n<br />\n老豆做走狗，仔女冇朋友！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c05aecbe5766f188f041a1e04f0f3bf74c611b15","tid":1636443,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:55:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n警察犯眾憎，老婆嗌離婚！<br />\n<br />\n老豆做走狗，仔女冇朋友！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"99bdf7a8892272617b815bbdafa43debabd9bb4e","tid":1636443,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:55:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-lar